									<p>
											At first my mom and sisters
and I made the mistake
											of putting him in a regular nursing home.
											It was really pretty;
											it had plush carpet
and afternoon art classes
											and a dog named Diane.
											But then I got a phone call.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
